-- SocGen Confirms 2010 Investment Bank Sales Target Assuming Normal Markets
-- Fabio Benedetti-Valentini
-- 2010-07-06T08:56:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-06/socgen-confirms-2010-investment-bank-sales-target-assuming-normal-markets.html

          
          
             Societe Generale SA’s corporate and
investment bank head Michel Peretie confirmed the CIB’s 2010
revenue target, assuming normal markets.  
 Speaking to reporters in Paris, he repeated that volumes
were soft in the second quarter.  
          
          


  


        